  "text": "The human cell lines HCT116, SW480 and 293T were purchased from the American Type Culture Collection (ATCC, Manassas, VA, USA). All cell lines were maintained in DMEM supplemented with 10% FBS (Gibco, USA) at 37°C, 95% humidity and 5% CO2. The SHMT2, HDM2, p53 and p53 mutant (NLS-, NES-) sequences [CITATION_1] were cloned into the ",
